node.text: Trevor is the most evolved human I’ve ever met. I have such a want to say something that means anything to anyone but I have no idea how to say it. He was dark and easy. Smart but optimistic. He was always the example of what I wanted to be. He has so many friends, a beautiful family and millions of fans. He is the big bro. The time he gave me was transformative. I am forever grateful. I’m so sad.

node.text: The second episode of HiLow season 2 is trending at #2 right behind @mrbeast. Me and 11 other people have been in the woods, climbing mountains and breaking trucks for the past five days shooting the finale. I’m really grateful that I get to do this for a living and even more grateful that a bunch of people want to watch it. Wait till you guys see the rest of this season.
